#: templates/about.html:278
msgid ""
"We specialize in multi-disciplinary engineering services with a particular "
"focus on high-stakes sectors like oil and gas infrastructure. Our reputation "
"is built on a foundation of technical excellence, rigorous safety standards, "
"and a commitment to delivering projects that stand the test of time."
